%^BOLD%^-=%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Mentalism Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

A caster with access to the mentalism domain is 
generally more aware of the powers of his mind 
than others are of theirs.  He is able to see 
for a short bit into the future with the aid of 
this domain as well as some distance away.

The mentalism domain contains the following spells:
Insight (3rd), Bolt of Force (5th), Inner Eye (8th)

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Kismet

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
     